OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773349951
OL,3,CHeathrow records busiest February
OL,4,Cafter 'bumper half-term'
OL,6,FHeathrow said it recorded its busiest
OL,7,FFebruary, with 5.8 million passengers
OL,8,Ftravelling through its four terminals
OL,9,Flast month.
OL,11,FThe figure was 110,000 more than the
OL,12,Fsame month last year, with the west
OL,13,FLondon airport attributing it to a
OL,14,F"bumper half-term combined with
OL,15,FChinese New Year travel".
OL,17,FHeathrow said the 1.9% increase was
OL,18,Fdriven by airlines operating larger
OL,19,Fand fuller aircraft.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@XO]
