PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773349951
OL,3,CHeathrow records busiest February
OL,4,Cafter 'bumper half-term'
OL,6,FIt warned that its two runways are
OL,7,F"full" and expressed concern its
OL,8,Fgrowth is "trailing the European
OL,9,Faverage" of 4.6%, saying it has lost
OL,10,Fits position as the continent's
OL,11,Fbusiest airport to Istanbul.
OL,13,FHeathrow said its plan to build a
OL,14,Fthird runway will "ensure the country
OL,15,Fgets the infrastructure it needs to
OL,16,Fstay competitive".
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@FO]pD@KOUqD@HO]vD@SOUxD@QO]
